What are the 5 Cadence Programming Language Pillars? Safety & security, Clarity, Approachability, Developer Experience, and Resource Oriented Programming
Safety & Security is essential for all users on either end of the Blockchain, so that trust can be built and confidence in interacting with a Smart Contract. Clarity is important for any level of blockchain expertise-user to be able to understand what is happening. Approachability is useful for users of any language being able to be familiar with the code. Developer experience is important for creating the smart contract in an efficient way for users to interact with said contract, and incase improvements can be made to create a better product.
